  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/6e72ba2705b54d3b551ca5d13644cd40.avif?t=1743751753\" width=400 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/468641df354df5a9a622fab106f8f4ce.webp?t=1743751753\" width=46 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a little rabbit, while reading the books of rabbit detective Flynn, Harold wanted nothing more than to become a rabbit detective himself!<br><br>And now, he is! <br>Together with his faithful sidekick, the bumblebee Maud, Harold will find anything that has been lost and misplaced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/2573f6955d1522499479168aa8e71ed2.avif?t=1743751753\" width=400 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But now, something has been stolen from Harold himself!  Will he be able to find out who did it, and why, and solve the mystery of ... <strong>the missing trumpet</strong>?<br><br>Find out in <strong>Harold Rabbit : Finder of Lost Things</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/468641df354df5a9a622fab106f8f4ce.webp?t=1743751753\" width=46 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Harold Rabbit : Finder of Lost Things</strong> is a fully hand-drawn point & click adventure for all ages, with an emphasis on fun and comedy.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/6e72ba2705b54d3b551ca5d13644cd40.avif?t=1743751753\" width=400 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/468641df354df5a9a622fab106f8f4ce.webp?t=1743751753\" width=46 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a little rabbit, while reading the books of rabbit detective Flynn, Harold wanted nothing more than to become a rabbit detective himself!<br><br>And now, he is! <br>Together with his faithful sidekick, the bumblebee Maud, Harold will find anything that has been lost and misplaced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/2573f6955d1522499479168aa8e71ed2.avif?t=1743751753\" width=400 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But now, something has been stolen from Harold himself!  Will he be able to find out who did it, and why, and solve the mystery of ... <strong>the missing trumpet</strong>?<br><br>Find out in <strong>Harold Rabbit : Finder of Lost Things</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3456340/extras/468641df354df5a9a622fab106f8f4ce.webp?t=1743751753\" width=46 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Harold Rabbit : Finder of Lost Things</strong> is a fully hand-drawn point & click adventure for all ages, with an emphasis on fun and comedy.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
